column1: Daily Weather Observations for Latrobe Valley, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3042.201603
Most observations from Latrobe Valley Airport, evaporation from Blue Rock Reservoir and sunshine from East Sale Airport.
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure, cloud and rainfall observations are from Morwell (Latrobe Valley Airport) {station 085280}
Evaporation observations are from Willow Grove (Blue Rock Reservoir) {station 085283}
